orth of Znamenka and pressed on to ward the junction The fall of Znamenka 45 miles southwest of Kremenchug would leave hundreds of thousands of German troops in the Dnieper Bend only a roundabout railway far to the south over which to escape Far to the north Gen Konstantin Rokossovsky drove the Germans from a commanding road junction northeast of Zhlobin and pinned them back against the Dnieper in a strategic vic tory presaging the capture of the White Russian rail hub front dis patches reported The attack neutral ized Dovsk which controls the Mogilev Gomel and KrichevBobruisk highways Hats In KM Rep Everett M Dirksen R Ill has announced his candidacy for the Republican presidential nomina tion Dirksen who is serving his sixth term in Congress released"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2025-04-13T08:27:12.153Z", "group": ["ndnp/dlc-2020_now", "library-of-congress-washington-dc-awardee-8"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn82016181/1943-12-03/ed-1/?sp=8", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_enfield_ver01:data:sn82016181:00516999974:1943120301:1196/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=338&w=233", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:dlc:batch_dlc_enfield_ver01:data:sn82016181:00516999974:1943120301:1196/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=677&w=467", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/dlc/batch_dlc_enfield_ver01/data/sn82016181/00516999974/1943120301/1196.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "washington", "district of columbia", "washington d.c."], "location_city": ["washington"], "location_country": ["united states"], "location_state": ["district of columbia"], "mime_type": ["image/jp2", "application/pdf", "text/xml", "image/jpeg", "image/jpeg", "application/json", "text/plain"], "number": ["1", "sn82016181", "5", "9", "6", "7", "4", "0", "0000000008"], "number_edition": ["1"], "nu